item.title: Privacy Policy for `Duplicates` add-on
item.description: Last updated: July 14th, 2023 This Privacy Policy describes how Duplicates handles and protects user information while using the add-on. Please read this policy carefully to understand how we collect, use, and safeguard your information. Information Collection: Duplicates does not collect any personal information or user data. The add-on operates entirely within the user’s Google Workspace environment and does not store or transmit any user information to external servers or databases.

item.title: Terms of Service for `Duplicates`
item.description: Last updated: July 14th, 2023 These Terms of Service (“Terms”) govern your use of Duplicates, an add-on developed by theOrganizedDev (“Developer”). By using the add-on, you agree to comply with these Terms. If you do not agree with these Terms, please refrain from using the add-on. Use of the Add-on: Duplicates is designed to help users identify and manage duplicate data within Google Sheets™. The add-on operates within the Google Sheets™ environment and is subject to the terms and conditions set by Google.
